<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Package Location Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-top: 4px solid #3182ce;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .location-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background-color: #3182ce;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .location-icon::after {
            content: 'üìç';
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .tracking-number {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3182ce;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .location-update {
            background-color: #ebf8ff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #bee3f8;
            position: relative;
        }
        .location-update::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            top: -8px;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background-color: #3182ce;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #ffffff;
        }
        .current-location {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2b6cb0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .update-time {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .estimated-arrival {
            background-color: #f0fff4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #48bb78;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3182ce, #63b3ed);
            width: 65%;
            border-radius: 4px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3182ce, #2c5aa0);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(49, 130, 206, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(49, 130, 206, 0.4);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .support-info {
            background-color: #fef5e7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f6ad55;
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .container { padding: 25px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="location-icon"></div>
        <h1>Package on the Move!</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>Your package is making progress! Here's the latest location update for your shipment. </p>

    <div class="tracking-number">
        Tracking Number: <%= trackingNumber %>
    </div>

    <div class="location-update">
        <div class="current-location">
             Current Location: <%= location %>
        </div>
        <div class="update-time">
            Last Updated: <%= updateTime %>
        </div>

        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-fill"></div>
        </div>

        <% if (estimatedArrival) { %>
            <div class="estimated-arrival">
                <strong>üïí Estimated Arrival:</strong> <%= estimatedArrival %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <p>Your package is on its way and we'll continue to keep you updated with real-time location information as it moves closer to its destination.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" class="button">Track Your Package</a>
    </div>

    <p>Thank you for choosing <%= appName %>. We're committed to keeping you informed every step of the way!</p>

    <div class="support-info">
        <strong>Questions?</strong><br>
        Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #d69e2e;"><%= supportEmail %></a> if you need assistance.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
    This email was sent regarding tracking number <%= trackingNumber %>
</div>
</body>
</html>